text.div:
ResourceProfileStatus

The lifecycle status of a Resource Profile

This value set defines its own terms in the system http://hl7.org/fhir/resource-profile-status

CodeDisplayDefinition
draftThis profile is still under development.
activeThis profile is ready for normal use.
retiredThis profile has been deprecated, withdrawn or superseded and should no longer be used.
